### Project: queryx — All 5 phases (Tasks #638-642)
Drop-in Go replacement for jmoiron/sqlx. Modern SQL extensions for database/sql: DB/Tx/Stmt/NamedStmt/Rows wrapping database/sql, reflectx struct field mapping with caching, named parameter binding (:name syntax with $1/?/@p1/:name formats), In clause expansion, generic Get[T]/Select[T] helpers, QueryError wrapping. Fixed sqlx bugs: Postgres ::type cast parsing, SQL comment handling. Context-first API, zero external deps, Go 1.22+, MIT. 63 tests with -race, MIGRATION.md, README.md. CI green.

